ed to realize. <br /> <br />SE did a horrible job at launch and they could have done much better. I don't think it comes to many peoples minds that SE DOES run passive programs that monitor our actions and bann people for seeming like a RMTer. My friend has gotten bann &quot;accidentally&quot; by this hidden system and her account was reactivated later on after she proved she wasn't an RMT. <br /> <br />I think seriously the problems with the markets right now is more that the players are abusing it beyond belief. I spent 3 hours trying to find items to make 1 item just now... even that lame website people setup is useless because its 4 days out of date with info on most of the items.  <br /> <br />It'll only get worse when SE doesn't listen to its players. <br /> <br />Personally I just think SE is being cheap and don't want to higher more people for their sad little &quot;special task force&quot; so they just try to make it a massive time sink which will only help the RMT more. When they are on at all hours of the day farming items to sell and most of us only get a few hours a day and it takes several of those hours to find items you want... yeah I think more people will buy gil in this game because of SE's flawed logic.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>RDM85 NIN85 BLU85 SMN85 WHM81 PLD75</div></div>
