 on what they do. After such an abysmal start, I don't think it will survive anymore botched ideas or partial fixes.  <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 25th 2010  1:29pm by mistrik </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Quote:</div><div class="orig">Pikko wrote: <br /><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Quote:</div><div class="orig"> sideways wrote: (really Pikko?)</div></div> <br />Oh go stuff that thread up your ass. Did you even READ that post? <br />[...] <br />I mean, excuuuuse me for trying to make people PLAY NICE.</div></div> <br /> <br />^ Second best forum mod smack down <b>*ever*</b>.</div></div>
